    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hey all, this blog post has been kicking around in my drafts for a while. I finally decided to complete it. It’s about thinking about compilation, basically the strategies and techniques that I’ve learned in my short time writing compilers. It’s what I wish I had as a resource when I started. <https://github.com/NicholasLYang/uptointerpretation/blob/master/content/posts/how-to-think-about-compiling.md>",
